影片在美国试映期间就获得了300万美元的收入，而其它国家的试映则达到400万美元<ref name="tino">Tino Balio, ''United Artists: The Company The Changed the Film Industry'', Uni of Wisconsin Press, 1987 p 231</ref>。

===专业评价===
根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上的13篇专业评论文章，本片保持者77%的好评度，并且根据网站上5315位观众的投票，85%的观众喜欢这部电影<ref name="rotten">{{cite web |title=A Man and a Woman |publisher=''Rotten Tomatoes'' |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_man_and_a_woman/ |accessdate=2013-04-19 |archive-date=2021-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211221112550/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/a_man_and_a_woman |dead-url=no }}</ref>

Bosley Crowther在其发表在《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的评论文章中认为本片拥有一流的摄影和感情真挚而强烈的配乐，两者结合堪称典范<ref name="nytimes">{{cite news|last=Crowther |first=Bosley |title=French and Frankly Romantic |publisher=''The New York Times'' |date=July 13, 1966 |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/review?res=940DE4DC1331E53ABC4B52DFB166838D679EDE |accessdate=April 1, 2012}}</ref>。

《[[综艺|综艺]]》杂志上对本片的评论文章则着重赞扬了主角的表演：“阿努克·艾梅拥有一种成熟的美丽和通过对内心情感的出色刻划来避免其角色平淡一面的能力。<ref name="variety">{{cite news|title=Un Homme et une Femme |publisher=''Variety'' |url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117791728?refcatid=31 |accessdate=April 1, 2012 |date=December 31, 1965}}</ref>”

